DOC.brief_summary: The aim of the study is to investigate the navigation of a newly developed catheter.
DOC.brief_title: Product Evaluation of a Newly Developed Intermittent Catheter.
DOC.criteria: 1. Male and at least 18 years 2. Has used Intermittent selfcatheterization at least 3 months 3. Has normal to slightly reduced hand mobility 4. Use catheter size CH12 or CH14 (must use same size during product evaluation) 1. Currently receiving treatment for urinary tract infection 2. Currently receiving chemotherapy
